text: Entry pt to old bkt timah railway station via alexandra/ queenway pcn.  Going south will reach tg pagar.  Well maintained pavement.  Go for both walk/ running/ cycling.
Good for family and group tracking, cycling in real natural place. Former Singapore to Malaysia railway so that you can see old rail bridge and stations along the corador.
Beautiful & convenient access to the Rail Corridor for bikes & pedestrians. Near various bus stops.

Nice walk :)
There are lots of benches and lots of places where u can buy refreshments (jelita etc)
